name: Top Knot - Matte Brown Tortoise - Prizm Sapphire Polarized

features: DESIGN: Top Knot is part of Oakley’s all-new Women’s Collection, designed to deliver the ultimate in fit and comfort in an on-trend design
SEE THE DETAILS: Available with Prizm™ lenses that are designed to enhance color, contrast and detail to make the most of any activity
LIGHTWEIGHT: O Matter™ frame material, combined with C-5 metal provides durability and all-day comfort to keep up with life on-the-go
PROTECTION: Protect your eyes like you protect your skin with a lens that offers 100% UV Protection
NO-SLIP: Comfortable Unobtainium® nosepads so the frame doesn’t slip off your face
COMFORT: Flexible spring hinges to help provide more comfort and durability
